  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_adult_comorbidity_evaluation_-_27">Adult Comorbidity Evaluation - 27</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_assessment_tool">ASSESSMENT TOOL</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
The 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_adult_comorbidity_evaluation_-_27">Adult Comorbidity Evaluation - 27</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_adult_comorbidity_evaluation_-_27">ACE-27</xref>
) is a 27-item comorbidity index for 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 with cancer.  It Identifies the important medical comorbidities and grade severity using the index.  </p>
